== Overview ==
"MegaCorp employee Reginald Klingoff was sitting at his desk one day, plodding away at his role as one of the corporation's many accountants. But Reginald had a dream. A dream that one day he would be famous for having invented one of the most powerful [[:Category:Weapons (Light Armor Piercing)|armor piercing weapons]] in history... shaped just like his pencil box (a present from his wife). Whilst in reality the now infamous armor piercing cannon has no relevance to his story, the Fire Blade still kicks arse big time. [Typically it fires 2B style shells]"

== Where to Acquire ==
The Fire Blade can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
